            <abstract>
                <p>Miracle of <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/> about the building of a church dedicated to St Gabriel in the country 
                    Neqlon/Niqlon with mentioning of a blind person, who asked about the completion of the work while the construction began. This 
                    miracle is very similar to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7196MGNiqlon"/> and thematically similar to 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7786SaneHomily"/>. According to the edition of 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Makweriya1976DersanaGabriel"/><citedRange unit="page">166</citedRange></bibl>,
                    it forms part of the monthly reading for the 19th of Gǝnbot in the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7815DersanaGa"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
